comments: Mr. Lewis is the best teacher I think I\'ve had in college so far. He makes class fun and exciting and it\'s really hard to not laugh in his classes. He is a very nice, sweet, funny man. He really does make Anthro interesting. He If you don\'t enjoy his class something is wrong with you. I don\'t like anthro but he makes it fun. TAKE HIS CLASSES

Best professor ever! I\'ve learned the most from him. He makes class fun. He really cares about his students and is more than willing to help them outside of the class room. He is also very funny it\'s hard to stop laughing. He is very intelligent.
